pageContext.claim: “We never had an empty seat. We went out and helped Ted Cruz. We went out and helped so many people. And I'll tell you what, if we didn't do those 32 rallies -- and it wasn't easy when you're doing rallies with 25, 30 thousand people.”
pageContext.analysis: There were empty seats at Trump's Houston rally with Cruz. "Many hundreds of seats were empty, including all of the boxes on both tiers of the mezzanine,” the Dallas Morning News reported.
